{"tid":1706920,"cid":14,"subCid":0,"title":"唔係個個都好似連登仔咁有錢","createTime":"2019-11-11T07:52:59.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-13T04:48:05.000Z","uid":108793,"like":26,"dislike":13,"uniUserReply":16,"replies":[{"pid":"0fc1cdee5b434c7e6d3cd55910a9ecbe7ef7c8e8","tid":1706920,"uid":108793,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-11T07:52:59.000Z","msg":"籌備充足之前唔應該貿然發起無限期三罷<br />\n<br />\n真正大三罷係需要好多時間籌備<br />\n工會先成立咗幾日<br />\n現實啲講都要養家 連糧食各樣都未儲好<br />\n<br />\n明白大家都好心痛好想報仇<br />\n但係咪應該要預備多一兩個月儲定糧先呢<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n籌備工會支援 請聯絡 @historywillabsolveme 或 @sellbbq<br />\n其他查詢 請聯絡 @proundtobehker 或 @sugdh<br />\n<br />\n🔴二百萬三罷聯合陣線🔴<br />\n抗爭 | 工會  | 罷工 | 行業行動<br />\n頻道 <a href=\"https://t.me/hkonstrike\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fhkonstrike&d=30k2sE%2FAiGmcVOPaBnjddT4xCSFqVWWaKp6LAuIW5iI%3D&h=6d878801\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/hkonstrike</a><br />\n公海 <a href=\"https://t.me/joinchat/FhM2GRbY1ThsEzrnbEyduA\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fjoinchat%2FFhM2GRbY1ThsEzrnbEyduA&d=30k2sE%2FAiGmcVOPaBnjddT4xCSFqVWWaKp6LAuIW5iI%3D&h=3bdf75ec\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/joinchat/FhM2GRbY1ThsEzrnbEyduA</a><br />\n各行業總Group list <a href=\"https://t.me/hkonstrike/222\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fhkonstrike%2F222&d=30k2sE%2FAiGmcVOPaBnjddT4xCSFqVWWaKp6LAuIW5iI%3D&h=be30ee94\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/hkonstrike/222</a><br />\nFB <a href=\"https://bit.ly/2JQLM2f\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F2JQLM2f&d=30k2sE%2FAiGmcVOPaBnjddT4xCSFqVWWaKp6LAuIW5iI%3D&h=48372b51\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://bit.ly/2JQLM2f</a><br />\nIG <a href=\"https://bit.ly/33hmGRR\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F33hmGRR&d=30k2sE%2FAiGmcVOPaBnjddT4xCSFqVWWaKp6LAuIW5iI%3D&h=17b8fbcb\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://bit.ly/33hmGRR</a>"},{"pid":